            "text": " one of the most financially ruining processes many must go through when separating from a failed marriage. Many wealthy people have had their fortunes significantly reduced while just trying to escape a relationship that is no longer worth pursuing. This is currently the case for one Robin Cannon, a multi-millionaire who made his fortune through a large home care service in the United Kingdom. His extensive collection of Bentley vehicles is widely regarded as one of the best collections in the ",
